description: Creates an Anycast static IP list.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: Name of the Anycast static IP list.

parameters.name: IpCount
parameters.description: The number of static IP addresses that are allocated to the Anycast static IP list. Valid values: 21 or 3.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: A complex type that contains zero or more Tag elements. Items (list) --- A complex type that contains Tag elements. (dict) --- A complex type that contains Tag key and Tag value. A string that contains Tag key. The string length should be between 1 and 128 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @. Value (string) --- A string that contains an optional Tag value. The string length should be between 0 and 256 characters. : / = + @.

nested_params.name: Items
nested_params.description: A complex type that contains Tag elements.

nested_params.name: Key
nested_params.description: A string that contains Tag key. The string length should be between 1 and 128 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: A string that contains an optional Tag value. The string length should be between 0 and 256 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @.

nested_items.name: AnycastIpList
nested_items.description: A response structure that includes the version identifier (ETag) and the created  AnycastIpList structure.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The ID of the Anycast static IP list.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the Anycast static IP list.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the Anycast static IP list. Valid values: Deployed, Deploying, or Failed.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Anycast static IP list.

nested_items.name: AnycastIps
nested_items.description: The static IP addresses that are allocated to the Anycast static IP list.

nested_items.name: IpCount
nested_items.description: The number of IP addresses in the Anycast static IP list.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The last time the Anycast static IP list was modified.

nested_items.name: ETag
nested_items.description: The version identifier for the current version of the Anycast static IP list.
